safenet.jhsm.misc

Class SCFS

  • java.lang.Object
    • safenet.jhsm.misc.SCFS_STATE
      • safenet.jhsm.misc.SCFS

  • public class SCFS
extends SCFS_STATE
    Class defining SCFS constants - Attribute constants.

    Further information concerning the various attribute types is provided in the ProtectServer Programmer's Manual.

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description

      The firmware has detected that there is a problem with hardware information section of the Flash ROM.

      The firmware has failed to detect the Real Time Clock.

      Newer hardware does not report anything in this interface.
      static SCFS TAMP_ACTIVE
      SRAM State indicates that the adapter has been tampered and the tamper is still active.

      The firmware has failed to detect the Serial port controller.
